The Old Deity of Xingxiu holds the realm in awe

25
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:08,220
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

26
00:02:08,220 --> 00:02:10,559
The Old Deity of Xingxiu holds the realm in awe

27
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:14,600
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

28
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:21,420
Out of my way, little monk!

29
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:23,080
You!

30
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:27,159
My master is tired and needs rest.

31
00:02:27,160 --> 00:02:29,499
So give him some space. Now scram!

32
00:02:29,499 --> 00:02:31,079
This pavilion is for everyone.

33
00:02:31,080 --> 00:02:33,900
- Why must we give it up to you?
- Fourth Brother.

34
00:02:33,900 --> 00:02:36,360
Don't bother with them.

35
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,020
Grand Martial Uncle.

36
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:49,040
Grand Martial Uncle, what brings you here?

37
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:51,800
Reverend, please come in.

38
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:16,280
Master, that's the monk who raises ice silkworms.

39
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:21,680
- Are you sure?
- Yes, I am.

40
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:25,040
I remember it well. It's him.

41
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:29,420
Grandmaster.

42
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:36,659
What happened to this young monk?

43
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,580
It hurts me to say this.

44
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:48,579
On this stretcher is my martial nephew.

45
00:03:48,579 --> 00:03:50,639
Due to our negligence,

46
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:54,479
he ran away from the monastery a year ago and did many misdeeds.

47
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:58,920
Until we finally found him and brought him back.

48
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:02,660
May I know who I'm talking to?

49
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:07,560
I am Ding Chunqiu.

50
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:11,340
You are the Head of the Dharma Academy, renowned for your Universe in the Sleeve, yes?

51
00:04:11,340 --> 00:04:14,280
It's an honor to meet you at last.

52
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:17,100
Hey. You there.

53
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:19,380
How did you get that helmet on your face?

54
00:04:19,380 --> 00:04:24,099
I've traveled all over the world, yet I've never seen such a guise.

55
00:04:26,040 --> 00:04:27,780
It was forced upon me.

56
00:04:27,780 --> 00:04:30,440
Who pulled such a prank on you?

57
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:34,339
A fine man like you doesn't deserve that mask.

58
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:38,619
Come here. I'll take it off of you.

59
00:04:38,619 --> 00:04:41,620
No! No...

60
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:18,400
Brother-in-Law, you're here.

61
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,420
Sit down.

62
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:26,579
I'm here to ask you about the man with the iron mask.

63
00:05:26,579 --> 00:05:29,039
Did you force him to wear the mask?

64
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:32,279
How could you do such a thing to him?

65
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:35,339
Brother-in-Law, don't be mad.

66
00:05:35,339 --> 00:05:39,419
The man with the iron mask is just a slave they brought here to keep me entertained.

67
00:05:39,419 --> 00:05:42,479
You even made him practice the Xingxiu Sect's venomous techniques?

68
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:45,180
You could've gotten him killed!

69
00:05:45,180 --> 00:05:48,900
He should be honored that I had him practice that.

70
00:05:48,900 --> 00:05:50,479
It shows that I think highly of him.

71
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:54,580
So what if he dies? I couldn't care less. His death doesn't matter.

72
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:03,000
Do you want to hit me?

73
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:10,340
Is that what you want?

74
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:12,199
You're going to slap me because of a slave?

75
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:14,240
That's a life!

76
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,740
How could you be so indifferent?

77
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,959
I promised your sister to raise you well

78
00:06:18,960 --> 00:06:21,079
so you wouldn't be led astray!

79
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:23,079
Your sister used to make fun of people and pull pranks on others, too.

80
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:24,799
But unlike you, she was thoughtful and considerate.

81
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,340
Why can't you learn from her?

82
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:31,119
You keep going on and on about my sister.

83
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:34,559
If you hate me so much, why bother about me then?

84
00:06:34,559 --> 00:06:39,139
Why don't you just leave me to the Xingxiu Sect and leave me be to fend for myself?

85
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:42,820
Get out!

86
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:16,500
[Xue Manor]

87
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:32,200
Reverend Xuan Nan of Shaolin and my acquaintances seek the Divine Physician Xue's assistance.

88
00:07:35,220 --> 00:07:36,720
Let's go inside.

89
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,560
Amitabha.

90
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:56,160
Greetings.

91
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:59,820
One of my companions is injured and requires the Divine Physician's immediate treatment.

92
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:01,580
He's better off left for dead.

93
00:08:01,580 --> 00:08:03,280
It has nothing to do with us.

94
00:08:03,280 --> 00:08:06,300
How cruel of you to say that.

95
00:08:13,615 --> 00:08:16,435
[Zither Maniac, Kang Guangling]

96
00:08:27,280 --> 00:08:32,700
Is your injured companion a monk?

97
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:37,759
Indeed, one of my disciples is injured.

98
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:48,660
You demon...

99
00:08:49,960 --> 00:08:51,360
Elder Brother!

100
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,120
Stop! Stop!

101
00:08:55,690 --> 00:08:57,100
[Respected]
(TN: used when someone has died)

102
00:08:58,760 --> 00:09:01,560
Stop!

103
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:04,540
Stop it.

104
00:09:04,540 --> 00:09:08,500
You got it all wrong.

105
00:09:08,500 --> 00:09:10,480
- Reverend Xuan Nan.
- Physician Xue.

106
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:13,920
We're all on the same side. Please, stand down.

107
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,199
We'll explain.

108
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,519
We are a group known as the Eight Friends of Hangu.

109
00:09:18,519 --> 00:09:21,719
This is the eldest among us, Kang Guangling.

110
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:24,239
I'm the fifth. You know our mentor.

111
00:09:24,239 --> 00:09:26,220
They call him the Intelligent Gentleman.

112
00:09:26,220 --> 00:09:28,880
The Intelligent Gentleman is deaf and mute.

113
00:09:28,880 --> 00:09:32,439
All of his disciples, too, are also deaf and mute.

114
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,380
Every martial artist knows that.

115
00:09:34,380 --> 00:09:37,820
But all of you are neither deaf nor mute.

116
00:09:37,820 --> 00:09:39,760
That's very strange.

117
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:43,280
Ding Chunqiu has a hand in this.

118
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,440
Everyone, let me explain.

119
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:48,180
Our founder once took in two disciples.

120
00:09:48,180 --> 00:09:51,319
The older of them was Su Xinghe, who is my mentor,

121
00:09:51,320 --> 00:09:54,480
and the younger was Ding Chunqiu.

122
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:58,580
Their martial arts skills were almost on par with each other.

123
00:09:58,580 --> 00:10:02,100
But my mentor was only interested in the fine arts,

124
00:10:02,100 --> 00:10:05,159
while Ding Chunqiu was focused on martial arts.

125
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:10,239
As the years passed, the gap between their mastery of martial arts widened.

126
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:14,320
He devoted half his life to mastering music and Go.

127
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:19,180
It's no wonder that Ding Chunqiu, who focused entirely on martial arts, would surpass him by far.

128
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:21,279
Ding Chunqiu excelled in martial arts so much

129
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:25,240
that he managed to wound our founder gravely and threw him into the ravine.

130
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,300
At the moment of such distress,

131
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,720
he unleashed the Qimen Dunjia Arts,

132
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,800
leading the duel to a deadlock.

133
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:34,520
At his dying breath,

134
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:38,280
our founder passed down the ultimate technique of our sect to our mentor.

135
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:41,199
Ding Chunqiu coveted our divine martial arts.

136
00:10:41,199 --> 00:10:43,660
He tried to extort them from our mentor.

137
00:10:43,660 --> 00:10:46,540
But he never said a word.

138
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:49,140
So, Ding Chunqiu had absolutely no way,

139
00:10:49,140 --> 00:10:53,479
but to force our mentor into a deal, in which he had to vow never to speak a single word

140
00:10:53,479 --> 00:10:55,620
if he were to be spared the worst.

141
00:10:55,620 --> 00:11:00,360
So my mentor wrote a letter

142
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:03,700
in which he dismissed and disavowed us as his disciples.

143
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:07,880
Since then, he has been feigning to be deaf and mute.

144
00:11:07,880 --> 00:11:09,519
I see.

145
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:12,619
We may have been dismissed,

146
00:11:12,619 --> 00:11:15,960
[Eight Friends of Hangu]
but we will never forsake his teachings.

147
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:18,720
Thus, we are collectively known as the Eight Friends of Hangu.

148
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:25,280
To honor the guidance and teachings taught to us by our mentor by the Hangu Pass.

149
00:11:29,260 --> 00:11:33,660
Martial Nephew Muhua, all you have to do is heal that monk, Hui Jing,

150
00:11:33,660 --> 00:11:35,400
and I shall spare your lives.

151
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:38,139
There's only one person in the world whose words I heed.

152
00:11:38,139 --> 00:11:40,860
I will only heal whoever he tells me to heal.

153
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:43,260
You can easily kill me if you wish.

154
00:11:43,260 --> 00:11:49,159
But to ask me to heal someone, you will need to beg our master for that!

155
00:11:49,159 --> 00:11:54,460
So, you heed no one but Su Xinghe. Am I right?

156
00:11:54,460 --> 00:11:56,479
Only a beastly scoundrel like you

157
00:11:56,480 --> 00:12:00,280
would show the idea of killing our mentor and then the rest of us!

158
00:12:14,640 --> 00:12:17,240
You've been poisoned. Hold your breaths!

159
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:20,059
You scoundrel Ding! Kill us if you want,

160
00:12:20,059 --> 00:12:23,839
but don't even think of forcing me to heal someone for you!

161
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:32,639
I'm going to ask you eight times, Muhua.

162
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:36,739
Will you heal this monk?

163
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:41,319
Each time you refuse,

164
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:44,580
I will kill one of your martial brethren.

165
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,679
I don't mind you killing me.

166
00:12:46,680 --> 00:12:49,739
If worse comes to worst, the eight of us will die together!

167
00:12:49,739 --> 00:12:52,160
You will die together?

168
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:56,801
I won't let you die.

169
00:12:56,801 --> 00:12:59,679
But when I ask my eighth time

170
00:12:59,680 --> 00:13:03,200
and you still refuse,

171
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:08,940
I might go and kill someone who calls themselves Intelligent Gentleman,

172
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:11,719
Su Xinghe.

173
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,079
You...

174
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,559
Don't you dare to lay a finger on my master!

175
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,420
Why wouldn't I dare to?

176
00:13:17,160 --> 00:13:21,219
The Old Deity of Xingxiu acts according to the whims of his temper.

177
00:13:21,219 --> 00:13:25,399
And you! You picked on my disciple.

178
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:27,479
So his master will have to fight back!

179
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,799
You...

180
00:13:28,800 --> 00:13:30,720
What's with the "you"?

181
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:35,460
Fine.

182
00:13:36,620 --> 00:13:38,960
I'll do as you say.

183
00:13:40,560 --> 00:13:45,260
But after I heal your monk,

184
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:47,460
you are not to harm any of my friends,

185
00:13:47,460 --> 00:13:50,060
my brethren, or my master!

186
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:14,500
A'Zi, I know you're still mad at me,

187
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:17,520
but you made a mistake in the first place.

188
00:14:18,640 --> 00:14:20,840
I had to make you understand.

189
00:14:20,840 --> 00:14:22,820
The Han are human.

190
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:24,599
And so are the Khitan.

191
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:27,260
We cannot bully the weak.

192
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:29,820
Neither can we toy with people's lives.

193
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,240
Do you understand?

194
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:35,680
I don't hear any movement inside.

195
00:14:35,680 --> 00:14:37,480
Could it be...

196
00:14:57,640 --> 00:14:59,140
Your Highness.

197
00:15:02,480 --> 00:15:04,400
Take a look at this.

198
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:07,740
[Don't come and find me, A'Zi]

199
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:13,320
Seriously, A'Zi.

200
00:15:14,160 --> 00:15:17,379
She hasn't fully recovered her skills, yet she fled to the Central Plains.

201
00:15:17,379 --> 00:15:19,640
She's asking for trouble.

202
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:22,420
Get me my horse. I'm going to find her.

203
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:23,940
No, Your Highness.

204
00:15:23,940 --> 00:15:26,319
This is no small matter for someone of your rank.

205
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:28,919
You can't just enter Song territory on your own.

206
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:31,119
Besides, our relations are complicated.

207
00:15:31,120 --> 00:15:33,319
We can't leave an opportunity for them to exploit.

208
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:35,679
If this creates unnecessary trouble,

209
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:38,140
that would be even harder to deal with.

210
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:41,279
Rest assured, Your Highness. I'll send someone to follow her discreetly right away.

211
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:43,199
Princess left without telling us.

212
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,499
If you go and find her yourself,

213
00:15:44,499 --> 00:15:47,720
she will likely refuse to show herself in your presence out of spite.

214
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,959
We have plenty of spies in Song.

215
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:51,479
I'll get them to find her.

216
00:15:51,480 --> 00:15:54,359
Give us a few days, and we'll find out where she is.

217
00:15:54,360 --> 00:15:57,760
All right. Do as you must.

218
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,260
She must be found.

219
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,820
Rest assured, Your Highness.

220
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,759
This one's gross!

221
00:16:15,760 --> 00:16:17,700
Take it back.

222
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,720
That stinks.

223
00:16:27,040 --> 00:16:28,199
Have a look, Miss.

224
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:30,519
These just came in today.

225
00:16:30,520 --> 00:16:32,199
This necklace is light in texture.

226
00:16:32,200 --> 00:16:34,219
This handkerchief is made of fine silk.

227
00:16:34,219 --> 00:16:36,260
It's selling well.

228
00:16:36,260 --> 00:16:38,700
Please buy one, Miss.

229
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,340
Come on, buy one.

230
00:16:41,340 --> 00:16:42,700
Princess.

231
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:44,959
- Princess.
- Princess.

232
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,800
Please come home with us now.

233
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,760
- Where's my brother-in-law?
- The prince is preoccupied with military affairs.

234
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:51,259
He simply could not leave.

235
00:16:51,259 --> 00:16:53,660
So he sent us to pick you up.

236
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:59,680
He can't even take a break to pick me up.

237
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:01,720
Why should I go back?

238
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:05,299
Does he want to lock me up just like last time?

239
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,719
Princess, you know how busy His Highness is.

240
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:10,279
Please don't make things harder for us.

241
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:12,719
Please just return with us.

242
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,639
Well, sorry.

243
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:18,460
It is in my blood to be deliberately provocative.

244
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:23,519
Go back and tell my brother-in-law

245
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:26,839
that if he doesn't apologize and pick me up in person,

246
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:29,720
I'll never go back.

247
00:17:29,720 --> 00:17:31,140
Farewell.

248
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:33,300
Princess.

249
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:45,119
The Old Deity of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss

250
00:17:45,120 --> 00:17:48,599
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

251
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:51,919
The Old Deity of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss

252
00:17:51,920 --> 00:17:55,439
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

253
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:58,719
The Old Deity of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss

254
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:02,119
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

255
