The Old Deity of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss

256
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:09,480
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

257
00:18:22,167 --> 00:18:23,879
[The Intelligent Gentleman, Su Xinghe]

258
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:27,179
The Old Deity of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss

259
00:18:27,179 --> 00:18:30,599
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

260
00:18:30,600 --> 00:18:33,959
The Old Deity of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss

261
00:18:33,960 --> 00:18:37,399
with his infinite strength and great magical power!

262
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:41,140
The Old Fairy of Xingxiu shall live in eternal bliss...

263
00:19:16,840 --> 00:19:19,719
We, the Eight Friends of Hangu, are here to visit you, Master.

264
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:23,799
We are infinitely delighted to see you in great health, Master.

265
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:28,099
Master, Reverend Xuan Nan of Shaolin is here to visit you, too.

266
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:38,040
Here you are, Reverend Xuan Nan.

267
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:41,460
So Mr. Deaf and Mute is neither deaf nor mute after all.

268
00:19:41,460 --> 00:19:44,960
I've sinned. I've sinned.

269
00:19:45,560 --> 00:19:48,120
Amitabha.

270
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:19,259
Your Zhenlong Go Formation is profound and ingenious.

271
00:20:19,259 --> 00:20:21,240
Even I cannot solve it.

272
00:20:21,920 --> 00:20:24,580
You are a meticulous young man.

273
00:20:24,580 --> 00:20:28,560
The moves you made were of advanced levels.

274
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:31,060
How could you not work out another move?

275
00:20:31,060 --> 00:20:32,920
What a pity.

276
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:40,079
The rest of you may get up as well.

277
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:42,020
Yes, Master.

278
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,119
Speaking about Zhenlong,

279
00:20:52,120 --> 00:20:55,439
I witnessed it in the cave at Wuliang Mountain the other day.

280
00:20:55,440 --> 00:21:00,339
This Intelligent Gentleman must have something to do with Sister Deity in the cave.

281
00:21:00,339 --> 00:21:04,559
I should ask him about it discreetly later.

282
00:21:07,200 --> 00:21:10,680
This round of Zhenlong has huge implications.

283
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,079
Bailing, come and take a look.

284
00:21:13,080 --> 00:21:15,119
If you managed to solve it somehow,

285
00:21:15,120 --> 00:21:17,900
it would be wonderful.

286
00:21:18,520 --> 00:21:20,380
Yes, Master.

287
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:32,659
Second, you're the Go expert.

288
00:21:32,659 --> 00:21:34,420
What is Zhenlong?

289
00:21:34,420 --> 00:21:38,620
Zhenlong is a difficult puzzle in Go.

290
00:21:38,620 --> 00:21:41,799
It is often a way to deliberately tease players

291
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:44,439
rather than a battle between two opponents.

292
00:21:44,440 --> 00:21:47,760
Therefore, no matter how hard you try,

293
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:49,840
it is often extremely difficult to deduce how to play next.

294
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:07,140
You're going to die in vain! Why take the trouble?

295
00:22:07,160 --> 00:22:09,239
That old scoundrel set up all of this

296
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:13,260
just to torment his victims to death.

297
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:17,959
Fan Bailing, you've walked right into the trap.

298
00:22:19,120 --> 00:22:21,500
What did you call our master just now?

299
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:27,399
The Deaf Mute Old Man is neither deaf nor mute for today.

300
00:22:27,400 --> 00:22:30,780
Surely you know why.

301
00:22:31,520 --> 00:22:33,839
Wonderful, wonderful!

302
00:22:33,840 --> 00:22:37,359
You broke your vows and sought your own doom.

303
00:22:37,360 --> 00:22:39,980
You can't fault me.

304
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:42,840
It took our master

305
00:22:42,840 --> 00:22:47,439
three years of hard work to perfect this Zhenlong game.

306
00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:51,999
Then, he sincerely invited all Go enthusiasts to solve the puzzle.

307
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,999
What an old fool I am.

308
00:22:54,000 --> 00:22:56,759
I delved into it for over 30 years,

309
00:22:56,760 --> 00:22:58,680
yet I could not solve it.

310
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:03,340
So, today, I sincerely invited all of you here to assist me.

311
00:23:03,340 --> 00:23:06,580
It will be a wish come true if any of you manages to solve it.

312
00:23:06,580 --> 00:23:11,179
Our master watching from the heavens will also find closure.

313
00:23:12,040 --> 00:23:14,079
Amitabha.

314
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:16,239
Such is the Intelligent Gentleman's intent

315
00:23:16,240 --> 00:23:19,999
that I believe that even his late master would be delighted to know.

316
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:22,560
Ding Chunqiu!

317
00:23:23,560 --> 00:23:27,759
This man is my martial junior.

318
00:23:27,759 --> 00:23:30,399
But he betrayed our master.

319
00:23:30,400 --> 00:23:33,860
He made him die with a grudge.

320
00:23:33,860 --> 00:23:37,499
I had wanted to follow after my master,

321
00:23:37,499 --> 00:23:42,000
but my late master had unfulfilled wishes.

322
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:45,840
Therefore, I survived to this day,

323
00:23:45,840 --> 00:23:48,460
enduring this humiliation.

324
00:23:50,040 --> 00:23:52,490
All these years,

325
00:23:52,490 --> 00:23:55,960
I had honored a pact with my junior

326
00:23:55,960 --> 00:23:59,280
not to speak a single word.

327
00:23:59,280 --> 00:24:01,380
I feigned to be deaf and mute.

328
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:05,420
Even my disciples, whom I just took in,

329
00:24:05,420 --> 00:24:11,780
I had to force them to be deaf and mute.

330
00:24:11,780 --> 00:24:14,060
It has been 30 years.

331
00:24:15,720 --> 00:24:17,820
No fruit had been borne.

332
00:24:18,920 --> 00:24:24,260
No one has ever been able to solve this Go puzzle.

333
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:28,000
Young Master Duan, whom I had a match with earlier,

334
00:24:28,000 --> 00:24:30,280
is a handsome and intelligent young man.

335
00:24:30,280 --> 00:24:34,080
His moves had been spectacular as well.

336
00:24:34,080 --> 00:24:38,219
But he failed to place the last piece and lost.

337
00:24:43,880 --> 00:24:45,159
Forgive my ineptitude.

338
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:49,360
I am truly humbled to be in your care.

339
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:09,740
I sense another great talent on his way.

340
00:25:09,740 --> 00:25:12,140
I am so overjoyed!

341
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:31,479
Young Master Murong, you're here to solve the Zhenlong puzzle.

342
00:25:31,480 --> 00:25:35,880
I hope you don't mind if I play on your behalf.

343
00:25:53,680 --> 00:26:00,139
I received an invitation to solve your puzzle, Intelligent Gentleman, during my journey.

344
00:26:02,240 --> 00:26:07,359
I could not resist dropping by to meet these fellow heroes.

345
00:26:08,360 --> 00:26:10,460
Amitabha.

346
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:20,740
Young Master Murong?

347
00:26:22,760 --> 00:26:26,620
Was Young Master Murong the one who placed that white chess piece?

348
00:26:26,620 --> 00:26:28,959
If Young Master Murong is here,

349
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,960
what about Miss Wang?

350
00:26:39,760 --> 00:26:41,239
Young Master.

351
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,479
What took you so long?

352
00:26:42,480 --> 00:26:44,879
The Old Freak of Xingxiu held us back on our way.

353
00:26:44,880 --> 00:26:47,360
We didn't expect to see him here.

354
00:26:49,040 --> 00:26:51,559
Both of them are as close as ever.

355
00:26:51,560 --> 00:26:54,400
There's no chance for me.

356
00:26:54,400 --> 00:26:59,199
Well, there was never a place for me in her heart.

357
00:26:59,200 --> 00:27:01,319
Even when she was alone with me,

358
00:27:01,320 --> 00:27:04,500
her cousin was all that was on her mind.

359
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:08,440
Young Master Duan.

360
00:27:11,040 --> 00:27:12,440
Are you doing well?

361
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:15,100
Do I look well to you?

362
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:18,000
What about you?

363
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:21,440
Young Master Duan, you're here too?

364
00:28:02,660 --> 00:28:03,899
Young Master Murong,

365
00:28:03,899 --> 00:28:07,119
you're good at martial arts, but as for chess...

366
00:28:07,120 --> 00:28:08,940
Not so much, I guess.

367
00:28:14,380 --> 00:28:16,820
You might not be able to win against me.

368
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:41,059
Young Master Murong, I don't see the need to play this anymore.

369
00:28:41,760 --> 00:28:45,059
Since you don't care about the Go game, why bother to mess around here?

370
00:28:45,059 --> 00:28:49,319
The Zhenlong Go formation is unsolvable, to begin with.

371
00:28:49,319 --> 00:28:51,839
I was just curious enough to drop by.

372
00:28:51,840 --> 00:28:55,699
I thought I would try it out to find out what was so peculiar about this game.

373
00:28:55,699 --> 00:28:57,680
Now that I have, I don't want

374
00:28:57,680 --> 00:29:02,220
to waste any more of my energy on this utter nonsense.

375
00:29:02,220 --> 00:29:04,400
Young Master Murong,

376
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:08,419
you can't even break free from being caught up with me.

377
00:29:08,419 --> 00:29:10,960
How can you win this challenge?

378
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:25,899
In terms of tactics and acumen,

379
00:29:25,899 --> 00:29:29,040
I still have the upper hand.

380
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:31,099
Murong Fu, Murong Fu.

381
00:29:31,099 --> 00:29:35,839
Do you want your family's reputation to crumble under your feet?

382
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:44,980
I'm out of luck.

383
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:47,580
It's all in vain.

384
00:29:47,580 --> 00:29:54,279
All my best efforts remain short-lived illusions in the end.

385
00:29:54,279 --> 00:29:57,040
It is all fate.

386
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:59,720
What more can I do?

387
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:04,900
You can't do that!

388
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,340
- Young Master!
- Young Master!

389
00:30:08,340 --> 00:30:09,980
Cousin!

390
00:30:11,600 --> 00:30:14,200
What an impressive execution of the Six Pulse Excalibur.

391
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:18,540
Young Master!

392
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:22,620
Cousin.

393
00:30:22,620 --> 00:30:25,239
It's all right if you can't solve the puzzle.

394
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,440
You don't have to kill yourself over it.

395
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:30,079
Young Master, this game fascinates the mind.

396
00:30:30,080 --> 00:30:32,319
I think there's an illusion to it.

397
00:30:32,320 --> 00:30:33,999
You mustn't delve too deeply into it.

398
00:30:34,000 --> 00:30:35,439
Luckily...

399
00:30:35,440 --> 00:30:36,519
just now....

400
00:30:36,520 --> 00:30:38,999
Young Master Duan staved off your fan.

401
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,260
I got caught up in the moment just now.

402
00:30:41,260 --> 00:30:43,560
It was as if I was possessed.

403
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:48,300
The Dali Duan clan's Six Pulse Excalibur surely lives up to its name.

404
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:49,999
You pulled me out from my moment of loss.

405
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:53,020
I can't thank you enough, Young Master Duan.

406
00:30:56,200 --> 00:31:00,160
Well, if it isn't one of the Dali Duan clan.

407
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:02,580
Pray tell, is it Duan Zheng Chun?

408
00:31:02,600 --> 00:31:05,719
Our boss is the true member of the Dali Duan clan!

409
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:08,280
The rest are all impostors!

410
00:31:16,040 --> 00:31:17,999
So my disciple is here, too.

411
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:21,919
The Four Evils are here to meet the Intelligent Gentleman.

412
00:31:21,919 --> 00:31:23,759
As per your invitation for a game of Go.

413
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:26,260
Welcome.

414
00:31:51,680 --> 00:31:53,720
Another one?

415
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:12,700
That was an excellent move.

416
00:32:12,700 --> 00:32:14,400
Let's see if you can solve it

417
00:32:14,400 --> 00:32:16,700
and break free from the formation.

418
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:38,300
Mr. Duan, your first few moves took you ahead.

419
00:32:38,300 --> 00:32:40,600
But your last was caught in a ruse.

420
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:43,400
A dead end. There's no way out.

421
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:46,400
You and your Shaolin Sect are orthodox indeed.

422
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:50,510
So tell me how would you solve it?

423
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:52,800
A Go formation is neither honest nor devious,

424
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:56,200
contrary to what it seems. You cannot solve it with honest moves.

425
00:32:56,200 --> 00:33:00,200
And neither can you do it with only unorthodox means.

426
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:39,000
Neither good nor evil, you say.

427
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,900
Never mind then.

428
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:45,400
You know what they say?

429
00:33:45,400 --> 00:33:47,000
It's easy to turn from good to bad,

430
00:33:47,020 --> 00:33:49,200
but hard to turn back to good.

431
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:52,000
One misstep, and you'll regret it for eternity.

432
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:55,400
By the time you look back, it's too late.

433
00:33:55,400 --> 00:33:58,400
As a royal heir of the Duan clan of Dali,

434
00:33:58,400 --> 00:34:02,400
I have fallen so far in the martial arts world.

435
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:06,000
I am ashamed to face my ancestors.

436
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:08,400
Ancestors?

437
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:12,000
Even if you die and go to the other world,

438
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:15,700
you wouldn't be able to face your ancestors.

439
00:34:15,700 --> 00:34:18,000
If you know you are ashamed,

440
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:20,200
why don't you end it all now?

441
00:34:20,200 --> 00:34:23,600
That's what a hero would do.

442
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:32,600
Why don't you just kill yourself?

443
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:35,700
Kill yourself!

444
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:44,200
Mr. Duan, no!

445
00:34:45,200 --> 00:34:48,400
Boss, catch that monk!

446
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,400
It's too late.

447
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:10,200
Duan Yanqing, hurry up and end it all!

448
00:35:10,200 --> 00:35:11,800
Indeed.

449
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:15,400
What's the point of living in this world any further?

450
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:18,000
I might as well end it all.

451
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:21,200
This Go challenge is driving people insane.

452
00:35:21,200 --> 00:35:23,600
If I could think of a way to distract him,

453
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,600
I might be able to save him.

454
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:29,600
I can't solve the game, but I can cause a commotion.

455
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:33,000
I... I'm going to solve it!

456
00:35:52,300 --> 00:35:54,200
You fool!

457
00:35:54,200 --> 00:35:56,000
You played in vain.

458
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:58,800
You killed a large chunk of your own white pieces.

459
00:35:58,800 --> 00:36:01,900
I know of no such move anywhere in this world!

460
00:36:07,200 --> 00:36:09,400
You brat.

461
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:11,100
You ruined my plans!

462
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:15,200
Old Freak of Xingxiu! You wanted to take advantage of this ruckus.

463
00:36:15,200 --> 00:36:18,100
I won't let you have it your way!

464
00:36:25,700 --> 00:36:28,800
Mr. Duan has been eliminated.

465
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:34,000
My late master has willed that anyone in the whole world is eligible to play.

466
00:36:34,800 --> 00:36:38,600
Your move, although whimsical

467
00:36:38,600 --> 00:36:42,000
it still counts as valid.

468
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:47,800
However, you eliminated a large number of your own pieces with that move.

469
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:50,600
If the black pieces close in on you,

470
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:53,400
how will you deal with it?

471
00:36:58,700 --> 00:37:00,600
Amitabha.

472
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:03,800
Senior, I'm not good at Go.

473
00:37:03,800 --> 00:37:07,900
I saw that Mr. Duan was disoriented by the game.

474
00:37:07,900 --> 00:37:10,000
That is why I made a move to distract him.

475
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:14,000
I will not make another move in this game.

476
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:16,000
I'm so sorry, Senior.

477
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:17,500
Stop!

478
00:37:18,400 --> 00:37:20,800
My master designed the Zhenlong Go formation

479
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:24,200
to invite chess masters from all over to solve it.

480
00:37:24,200 --> 00:37:28,200
It's not a big deal if it can't be solved.

481
00:37:29,200 --> 00:37:32,000
But if anyone deliberately messes it up

482
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:35,500
and put all of his effort to waste,

483
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:38,600
even if that person were to bring thousands of troops,

484
00:37:38,600 --> 00:37:43,000
I will fight to the death with that person!

485
00:37:52,600 --> 00:37:55,200
- But Senior...
- Play on!

486
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:59,000
My master's efforts are not something you can toy with.

487
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:44,200
Lower left, 3-9.

488
00:38:44,200 --> 00:38:45,600
Who was that?

489
00:38:45,600 --> 00:38:47,600
Who's teaching me to play?

490
00:38:50,100 --> 00:38:52,300
Who spoke to me?

491
00:38:57,800 --> 00:39:01,000
Forget it. I'll just do as told.

492
00:39:13,400 --> 00:39:16,800
Lower left, 2-8.

493
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:51,200
Upper right, 5-6.

494
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:24,600
Even I can figure out these few moves.

495
00:40:24,600 --> 00:40:27,000
But everything is hard at first.

496
00:40:27,000 --> 00:40:31,000
I never expected the first move.

497
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:37,600
Cousin? This is just a game of Go.

498
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:40,000
Why do you care so much?

499
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:49,200
Upper left, 7-8.

500
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:22,200
Little monk, you are indeed gifted.

501
00:41:23,400 --> 00:41:26,800
30 years have passed

502
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:29,600
since my master set up this formation,

503
00:41:29,600 --> 00:41:32,000
and no one has ever been able to solve it.

504
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:39,500
Until today, when you came and solved it.

505
00:41:39,500 --> 00:41:43,200
Senior, I did it?

506
00:41:44,200 --> 00:41:46,800
I am truly grateful to you.

507
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:49,400
No, no, Senior. You got it all wrong.

508
00:41:49,400 --> 00:41:51,800
Actually, it wasn't me. It was...

509
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:55,200
This is a secret. Don't tell anyone.

510
00:41:55,200 --> 00:41:58,500
Otherwise, your life will be at risk.

511
00:41:59,400 --> 00:42:03,900
Actually, Senior, I only got lucky.

512
00:42:03,900 --> 00:42:06,400
You're flattering me.

513
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:11,200
Young Monk, please.

514
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:14,200
That's the gateway to my sect!

515
00:42:14,200 --> 00:42:18,000
How dare you try to tread on it, you bald brat!

516
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:50,000
